        "message": "Patch Set 14:\n\nI cannot reproduce this in my local testing (it is not a Helm based system though so it is not exactly the same).  One previous experience we had the same problem was due to quoting around the list of nodes (IP:port), -- the command expects a list of arguments, not single argument with space between. Since I do not know how Helm does the processing here I do not know whether this applies here.  So just adding a paste processing to see if this fixes the problem.",
